The '''Tax Levy Bill''' was a bill debated by the [[Galactic Senate/Legends|Galactic Senate]] sometime between the [[Invasion of Naboo/Legends|Invasion of Naboo]] and the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. It proposed raising taxes to help deal with [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] raiding [[Hyperlane|hyperroutes]]. However, some feared that the money would be used for less important measures. [[Jar Jar Binks/Legends|Jar Jar Binks]] voted against it.

